sequenceDiagram
    participant SK as Spec Kit
    participant PF as Plan Forge
    participant AI as AI Agent
    participant RV as Reviewer

    SK->>SK: /speckit.specify → spec.md
    SK->>SK: /speckit.plan → plan.md
    SK->>SK: /speckit.tasks → tasks.md
    SK->>PF: Auto-import artifacts
    PF->>PF: Harden into execution contract
    PF->>PF: Add Forbidden Actions + Gates
    PF->>AI: Execute slice-by-slice
    AI->>AI: Build + Test gate per slice ✓
    AI->>RV: Hand off to independent review
    RV->>RV: Fresh session audit
    RV->>PF: Ship ✅
